AdditionalAttributes.description:
- Ready in minutes
- Eat with protein of choice for a quick lunch or dinner.
- 1 steam bag = 2 of your 5 recommended serves of vegetables every day.
- Source of Vitamin C to support immune system function
- Source of Vitamin A and fibre.
- Snap Frozen: Our vegetables are picked at their prime, then lightly blanched, before being snap frozen. This locks in taste and natural vitamins & minerals, so your family get them as nature intended.

Birds Eye SteamFresh Carrot, Broccoli & Corn Mix adds great colour, flavour and a healthy touch to all your favourite meals. Quick and easy to prep, this is a nutritious staple to keep in the freezer.

Cut down food prep time with Birds Eye Carrot, Broccoli & Corn Mix. Made with a selection of snapfrozen, crisp veggies packed in three individual steam bags, this is a convenient way to whip up a side dish or bulk up your veggie intake alongside a roast. You'll love just how quick you can prep this.

A classic combination of veggies, Heinz Steam Fresh Broccoli, Carrots & Cauliflower takes the fuss out of meal prep. Simply steam in the bag and enjoy these veggies with locked in flavour. Whether you only have a quick break for lunch or you're tired after a long day, Heinz Steam Fresh Broccoli, Carrots & Cauliflower is the easy way to pack your plate with vegetables. Picked at their peak, frozen and sealed in individual steamer bags, these veggies are ready to be enjoyed at any time of the year. Each Heinz Steam Fresh bag contains two serves of veg† and as part of a healthy, varied diet, the veggies in this bag naturally deliver folate and vitamin C, vitamin A and provide a source of dietary fibre.
